# GUI Vue Component Pattern

Use Options API with `inject` for RPG-JS services. Close via `rpgGuiClose('gui-name')` so the name matches the GUI id.

```vue
<template>
    <div class="my-gui">
        <!-- Content -->
    </div>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
export default {
    name: 'my-gui',
    inject: ['rpgEngine', 'rpgKeypress', 'rpgGuiClose', 'rpgGui', 'rpgStage'],
    props: ['propName'],
    mounted() {
        // Initialize
    },
    methods: {
        close() {
            this.rpgGuiClose('my-gui')
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
.my-gui { }
</style>
```
